room_title: Escape room "Murder on 155" by One Way Out in Tyler
review: We didn't solve the Murder on 155 but we came close and it was lots of fun. I recommend this activity for family fun.

room_title: Escape room "Murder on 155" by One Way Out in Tyler
review: Brought another couple and had a great time. We escaped from the "Murder Mystery" room with 13 minutes to spare. Not bad!Very well thought out room with some challenging puzzles.

room_title: Escape room "Murder on 155" by One Way Out in Tyler
review: We had an amazing time! The customer service was wonderful and we will definitely be back! If you are looking for a date night with a group of friends, this is the spot! Murder on 155 ROCKED!
